text: Mjölby Turabdin FC is a Swedish football club located in Mjölby. ==Background== Mjölby Turabdin FC currently plays in Division 4 Östergötland Västra which is the sixth tier of Swedish football. They play their home matches at the Kungshögaplan in Mjölby.
